Name: Moo Moo Move
About the game: DESCRIPTION MOO MOO MOVE is a casual arcade game about guiding chubby cows to safety. Players drive the herd through a host of cute floating islands built with a country feel. UFOs, poachers, ice and more stand between the cows and their next meal - it's down to the player to get them there! HISTORY MOO MOO MOVE began as a Tranzfuser project in 2017, where it was awarded funding for its continued development. It is the first game to be released by graduate team MOCHI MODE. FEATURES Unique hand-painted island levels. A host of hazards to tackle. Cute visuals that make you feel relaxed. 8 round cows just looking for a snack! Now in Welsh, Swedish, Norwegian and Chinese (Simplified)
